* 2011年11月1日開通。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/11/10/30/n3415833.htm%E6%97%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7--%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E5%B9%B4%E8%B2%BC1500%E8%90%AC.html |title=旗美快捷 高市年貼1500萬 |accessdate=2015-11-25 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115710/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/11/10/30/n3415833.htm%E6%97%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7--%E9%AB%98%E5%B8%82%E5%B9%B4%E8%B2%BC1500%E8%90%AC.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
